## Item Deleter

Periodically sweeps your inventory and deletes specific items. Out of
the box, it doesn't delete anything. Specify which items to delete by
going to `Actions > Init` custom code. Then add item names or IDs
to `itemList`.

**Dev status**: Release

**Classes**: All

**Requested by**: Arc
